Minor changes (0-3 months)
--------------------------

init:
	- don't restart jgmenu on setting theme
	- add command to amend (and possibly --dry-run)

greeneye:
	- shorten searchbox so that the ...s do not clash with the icon

ob: set ^tag() to command rather than name to reduce risk of duplication

Trim argv-buf fields on parse

pmenu: handle .desktop override $XDG_DATA_DIRS without showing duplicates

jgmenu - warn if strange command line argument is given
